    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あなたを一人にはしない。だから、もう……\n私の前から、勝手にいなくならないで！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't leave you alone. So…\nDon't just disappear from me!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある日のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0999995549
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0999995549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私に……映画のお仕事ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A movie job… for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.966666158,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6933.333841999998,
          "startTime": 20.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "アクション映画のオファーが来てるんだ\nこれが資料なんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s been an offer for an action movie.\nHere are the materials.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6919035912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、漫画が原作の映画で\n私の役は……え、主人公！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚  it’s a movie based on a manga…\nAnd my role is… Huh? The main character!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1919040998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.5585689863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、主人公はプロのバイクレーサーの娘で\n高校生ながらにレースクイーンをしている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚  the main character is the daughter of a pro motorcycle racer…\nand she works as a race queen while she’s in high school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9919028283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女自身も幼い頃からバイクを楽しんでいたが\n十年前のレース中の事故で、父が亡くなってしまうんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s loved motorcycles since she was little‚  but…\nher father died in an accident during a race ten years ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2969814302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、父が大好きだったバイクに乗りたくても\n事故を目の前で見ていたトラウマで乗れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So even though she wants to ride the motorcycle her father loved so much…\nbut she can’t ride it because of the trauma of seeing the accident…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7471522318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、少しでも父の近くにいたいから\nレースクイーンをしている……と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she still wants to be close to her father‚  so…\nshe works as a race queen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6969819388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8636480969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "辛い過去を背負っても強く生きる高校生……か\n素敵な役ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A high school student who lives strongly even while carrying a painful past…\nIt’s a wonderful role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4303152722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6303147635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんで演技の経験もないのに\n私にオファーが来たんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why would they offer it to me…\nwhen I have no acting experience?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9303152722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6636480969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "演技なら沙季とか、もっと向いている人がいますし……\n最近だと葵さんもドラマに出演していましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-san would be much better suited for acting‚  or…\nEven Aoi-san has been in a TV series recently‚  right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8624649768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや……実は、最初は葵に話が来たんだが\n枠が空いていた悪役をやりたいと言い出してな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… Actually‚  the offer did go to Aoi at first‚  but…\nshe said she wanted to play the villain‚  since there was an opening…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.7354395551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんらしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds just like Aoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7354395551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、主人公役をどうするか相談した結果\n琴乃にやってもらえないかという話になったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚  as a result of discussions about what to do with\nthe main character role… The idea came up to ask you to play it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "原作のイメージにぴったりだし、綺麗な黒髪だから\nバイクで疾走する姿も映えそう……と先方が乗り気でな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They thought you’d fit the image perfectly with your beautiful black hair…\nThey think you’d look great speeding on a motorcycle… they’re quite enthusiastic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.2720608078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗な黒髪……映えそう……なるほど\nそんな風に評価してもらえるんですね。なるほど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Beautiful black hair… I'd look great… I see.\nSo that’s how they see me. I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.6663476194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9720608078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、演技の経験がないうえにバイクも乗った\nことないですよ？　本当に大丈夫なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… But I have no acting experience‚  and I've never even ridden\na motorcycle before? Are you sure it’ll be alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4700068797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5387274745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこはしっかり教えてもらうから安心してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll learn everything properly‚  so don’t worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5387274745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュール的にはなんとかなるし\n後は琴乃のやる気次第だが……どうしたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can work the schedule out‚\nand the rest depends on your motivation… What do you want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8791808926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "サポートしてもらえるのであれば……やってみたいです\nこんな機会、なかなかいただけませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re going to support me… I want to try it.\nThis kind of opportunity doesn’t come around often.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2458480679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.7791808926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。それじゃあ先方に伝えておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I’ll let them know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7791808926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
